Georges Paulais https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Georges_Paulais 0 Georges Paulais (16 September 1884 – 12 December 1967) was a French film actor. He appeared in 145 films between 1910 and 1956. He was born in Guimps, Charente, France and died in Chabanais, Charente, France. Georges_Paulais ( 16_September_1884 – 12_December_1967 ) was a_French_film_actor .
